🎯 Demo Summary
===============
This effort (fallback-strategies) provides:
• FallbackManager for orchestrating fallback mechanisms
• FallbackStrategy interface with multiple implementations
• InsecureHandler for --insecure flag management
• Retry logic with exponential backoff
• Graceful degradation for certificate validation failures
• Warning system for security implications
• Integration with certificate validation pipeline
• Registry-specific insecure mode support

🔧 Key Features Demonstrated:
• Certificate validation fallback strategies
• Insecure mode for development environments
• Retry mechanisms for transient failures
• Security warning notifications
• Registry trust store integration

